{
  "texts": [
    "For each snippet, we collect two Agency annotations (one for each designer; 454 * 2 = 908 total) as discussed next.",
    "Let C i be a conversational snippet b/w designers D i1 and D i2.",
    "Then, for each D ij ∈ {D i1, D i2 }, our goal is to annotate the Agency level and the expressed Intentionality, Motivation, Self-Efficacy, and Self-Regulation of D ij in C i.",
    "Annotating Agency.",
    "To get annotations on Agency, we leverage the end-of-study questionnaire filled by the interior designers (Section 5.1)."
  ]
}